data.description: Beautiful farmhouse style home complete with a rocking chair front porch, an open floor plan and finished 3rd floor suite! Inside, you'll immediately notice the modern touches including, LVP flooring throughout, 9ft ceilings, and attractive wainscotting in the foyer and formal dining room. The main living area is bright and airy and perfect for entertaining. The living room features a fireplace with space to add built-ins on either side and double sliding French patio doors. Highlights of the striking kitchen include white cabinets, countertops, and subway tile backsplash, stainless appliances, large island with bar seating, breakfast nook, and pantry. A guest bedroom and full bath are located just off the kitchen. Upstairs, you'll find a large owner's suite with a huge walk-in closet and a spa-like bath complete with dual sinks, tiled walk-in shower, and soaking tub. Two additional bedrooms, a separate full bath as well as an additional bonus room provide space for your family and guests. The laundry room is also conveniently located on the 2nd floor. Hidden stairs lead up to the 3rd floor. The large bonus room and full bath make nice separate quarters. Enjoy the outdoors from the comfort of the screened in porch. The garage has built-in cabinetry to help keep all of your outdoor things organized. The community features an outdoor pool and is located near the public boat ramp, Kiwanis park and fabulous Topsail Beach. Come see this home today!Seller NOW offering $5000. use as you choose to buyer.
